docs.title: Quansheng UV-K5 – Documentation
docs.text:
Welcome ! This site contains : - High level documentation to explain how the firmware works - Low level documentation detailling variables and functions - Some "How to" to ease firmware development ex : - How to manage the menu (create item, create sub menu etc.) - How to store information in the eeprom - How to modify VFO information (frequency, mode, tx power, squelch) - ...

👉 Reference : Doxygen
